# Loyalty — Cron Expiry Warning Trigger (M11-S06)
# GCP Cloud Scheduler fires this once a week (Mondays 06:00 UTC).
# Publishes one PointsExpiringSoon event per customer with points expiring within 7 days.
# In production this is called by GCP Cloud Scheduler (network-protected).
# M115-S03 adds CronAuthGuard (OIDC token from GCP Cloud Scheduler).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /cron/loyalty-expiry-warning — run weekly expiry warning
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/loyalty-expiry-warning

###

### POST /cron/loyalty-expiry-warning — expect 200 { customersNotified: 0 } when no expiring entries
# (no entries in DB with expires_at within next 7 days)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/loyalty-expiry-warning

###
